{"tid":1491642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"來自一群信報小薯","createTime":"2019-08-20T13:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T14:48:14.000Z","uid":122607,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dfda5643cc8f6a7959f1d247e0412206c823fa87","tid":1491642,"uid":122607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:29:13.000Z","msg":"代信報朋友放：<br />\n<br />\n對於副刊同事在將軍澳連儂牆遇襲受傷，我們感到切膚之痛。希望社會各界與我們一起，祝福同事早日康復。<br />\n<br />\n作為信報及社會一分子，不論身分地位、辭職與否，同樣享有和平自由表達意見的權利，我們譴責任何威脅言論自由的暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n接連發生威脅言論自由的暴力行為，社會上彌漫著白色恐怖，我們寄望政府能正視並解決問題，及警方能真正做到嚴正執法，不偏不倚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一群信報小薯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0TQVjbq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0TQVjbq.jpg&h=d424001a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7b3d946a9e1bc9da316624d08e5a799eca0760b","tid":1491642,"uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:33:17.000Z","msg":"唉<br />\n咩撚野世界<br />\n仲話香港係最安全城市 我屌咩..."},{"pid":"6e19e0b221ea0cdf27b822347dc65d7fd4092c76","tid":1491642,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7b3d946a9e1bc9da316624d08e5a799eca0760b","tid":1491642,"uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:33:17.000Z","msg":"唉<br />\n咩撚野世界<br />\n仲話香港係最安全城市 我屌咩..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:34:25.000Z","msg":"斬人個個未最安全囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8dc3882db222d83e190914440b6ba1220f2918c","tid":1491642,"uid":281199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fdf323408513dca304405fa03bb26bb2fa1769","tid":1491642,"uid":175159,"